node.text: @throughlucaslens you are welcome 🙏🏼 Happy to discover your feed . Fantastic photos

The Chongqing region is known for its impressive bridges that span the Yangtze and Jialing rivers, connecting the city's hilly terrain with stunning architectural designs.

#china #chongqing #重庆市 #photography #yangtze #architecture #architectureanddesign
This bridge looks so cool bro🔥
@throughlucaslens you are welcome 🙏🏼 Happy to discover your feed . Fantastic photos
@myahya09 Thank you! I was also amazed – what they've done there is truly stunning! 🤩 More content is coming soon, so stay tuned Bro! 🙌
I'm just amazed at how Chongqing is an actual city, and not something fictional.. Truly amazing what they've done over there!!!!!
